data.description: Welcome to 968 East I Street, a charming single-story home nestled in a good neighborhood in North Ontario. This well-maintained residence offers a prime location, conveniently close to a nearby park, the Ontario International Airport, and the 10 Freeway. This house has been meticulously kept throughout with great curb appeal. The updated kitchen is a highlight, providing modern amenities for culinary enthusiasts. Featured pony wall opens to the Living room so the home continues to feel open and flowing. The home features a spacious layout with four bedrooms and two bathrooms, offering ample room for comfortable living. You will find lots of built in cabinets for extra storage. Outside, enjoy the serenity of the property adorned with fruit trees, creating a delightful outdoor atmosphere. Whether you're looking for a family home or a cozy retreat, 968 East I Street is a must-see for those seeking a combination of convenience, style, and a touch of nature. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
